---
By: Sivananda
Locus:
  Page: 181
  Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Giving
---
The best thing to give your enemy is forgiveness; to an opponent,
tolerance; to a friend, your heart; to your child, a good example; to your
father, deference; to your mother, conduct that will make her proud of you;
to your self, respect; to all men, charity.
